{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.1","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:1","prev_osis_id":"Exod.023.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Mo\u00efse sur la montagne de Sina\u00ef<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-8: cf. Jos 24:22-27. H\u00e9 9:18-23. (2 Ch 15:11-15.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Dieu dit \u00e0 Mo\u00efse: Monte vers l\u2019\u00c9ternel, toi et Aaron, Nadab et Abihu, et soixante-dix des anciens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et vous vous prosternerez de loin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.2","name":"Exode 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.23.33","name":"Exode 23:33","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.23.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.2","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:2","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Mo\u00efse s\u2019approchera seul de l\u2019\u00c9ternel; les autres ne s\u2019approcheront pas, et le peuple ne montera point avec lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.3","name":"Exode 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.1","name":"Exode 24:1","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.3","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:3","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Mo\u00efse vint rapporter au peuple toutes les paroles de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et toutes les lois. Le peuple entier r\u00e9pondit d\u2019une m\u00eame voix: Nous ferons tout ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel a dit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.4","name":"Exode 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.2","name":"Exode 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.4","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:4","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Mo\u00efse \u00e9crivit toutes les paroles de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Puis il se leva de bon matin; il b\u00e2tit un autel au pied de la montagne, et dressa douze pierres pour les douze tribus d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.5","name":"Exode 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.3","name":"Exode 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.5","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:5","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il envoya des jeunes hommes, enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, pour offrir \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel des holocaustes, et immoler des taureaux en sacrifices d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.6","name":"Exode 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.4","name":"Exode 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.6","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:6","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Mo\u00efse prit la moiti\u00e9 du sang, qu\u2019il mit dans des bassins, et il r\u00e9pandit l\u2019autre moiti\u00e9 sur l\u2019autel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.7","name":"Exode 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.5","name":"Exode 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.7","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:7","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Il prit le livre de l\u2019alliance, et le lut en pr\u00e9sence du peuple; ils dirent: Nous ferons tout ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel a dit, et nous ob\u00e9irons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.8","name":"Exode 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.6","name":"Exode 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.8","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:8","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Mo\u00efse prit le sang, et il le r\u00e9pandit sur le peuple, en disant: Voici le sang de l\u2019alliance que l\u2019\u00c9ternel a faite avec vous selon toutes ces paroles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.9","name":"Exode 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.7","name":"Exode 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.9","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:9","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-11: cf. (\u00c9z 1:26-28. Ap 4:2-6.) Ex 33:18-23. (Mt 5:8.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Mo\u00efse monta avec Aaron, Nadab et Abihu, et soixante-dix anciens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.10","name":"Exode 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.8","name":"Exode 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.10","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:10","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Ils virent le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; sous ses pieds, c\u2019\u00e9tait comme un ouvrage de saphir transparent, comme le ciel lui-m\u00eame dans sa puret\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.11","name":"Exode 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.9","name":"Exode 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.11","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:11","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Il n\u2019\u00e9tendit point sa main sur l\u2019\u00e9lite des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Ils virent Dieu, et ils mang\u00e8rent et burent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.12","name":"Exode 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.10","name":"Exode 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.12","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:12","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-18: cf. De 9:9-11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Mo\u00efse: Monte vers moi sur la montagne, et reste l\u00e0; je te donnerai des tables de pierre, la loi et les ordonnances que j\u2019ai \u00e9crites pour leur instruction.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.13","name":"Exode 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.11","name":"Exode 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.13","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:13","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Mo\u00efse se leva, avec Josu\u00e9 qui le servait, et Mo\u00efse monta sur la montagne de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.14","name":"Exode 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.12","name":"Exode 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.14","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:14","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Il dit aux anciens: Attendez-nous ici, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que nous revenions aupr\u00e8s de vous. Voici, Aaron et Hur resteront avec vous; si quelqu\u2019un a un diff\u00e9rend, c\u2019est \u00e0 eux qu\u2019il s\u2019adressera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.15","name":"Exode 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.13","name":"Exode 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.15","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:15","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Mo\u00efse monta sur la montagne, et la nu\u00e9e couvrit la montagne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.16","name":"Exode 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.14","name":"Exode 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.16","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:16","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>La gloire de l\u2019\u00c9ternel reposa sur la montagne de Sina\u00ef, et la nu\u00e9e la couvrit pendant six jours. Le septi\u00e8me jour, l\u2019\u00c9ternel appela Mo\u00efse du milieu de la nu\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.17","name":"Exode 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.15","name":"Exode 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.17","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:17","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.024.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>L\u2019aspect de la gloire de l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e9tait comme un feu d\u00e9vorant sur le sommet de la montagne, aux yeux des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.18","name":"Exode 24:18","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.16","name":"Exode 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.18","label":"","reference":"Exode 24:18","prev_osis_id":"Exod.024.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.025.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.24.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Mo\u00efse entra au milieu de la nu\u00e9e, et il monta sur la montagne. Mo\u00efse demeura sur la montagne quarante jours et quarante nuits.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.24","name":"Exode 24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.25.1","name":"Exode 25:1","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.25.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.24.17","name":"Exode 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.24.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81ede6882d0.04661310');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81ede6882d0.04661310\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81ede6882d0.04661310","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81ede6882d0.04661310'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81ede6882d0.04661310\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}